nodes.text: The Mar Duun was a CR90 corvette used by the Rebel alliance. The Mar Dunn, along with the Vop Hui, attempted to disrupt a meeting involving TIE Defender prototypes being transferred to the Escort Carrier Hininbirg by deploying mines around the transfer point. However, the Mar Duun and the Vop Hui were destroyed along with the minefield by Imperial Ace Maarek Stele.
